### Public Pay Link (Staff: create session link)
POST {{baseUrl}}/reservations/{{reservationId}}/public-pay-link/square
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventDate": "{{eventDate}}",
  "ttlMinutes": 20
}

###
### Public Pay Session (Client page bootstrap)
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/pay-session?eventDate={{eventDate}}&reservationId={{reservationId}}&token={{publicPayToken}}

###
### Public Pay Charge (Client completes payment)
POST {{baseUrl}}/public/pay-session/charge
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventDate": "{{eventDate}}",
  "reservationId": "{{reservationId}}",
  "token": "{{publicPayToken}}",
  "sourceId": "{{squareSourceId}}"
}
